lopment of tuberculosis in patients who tested negative for latent tuberculosis infection prior to initiating therapy.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/470/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Velpatasvir, Rilpivirine, More', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Belimumab, More', 1767369485);
